title: Breaking: Death investigation underway near 22nd and Wisconsin Avenue in Milwaukee
content:
×  Breaking: Death investigation underway near 22nd and Wisconsin Avenue in Milwaukee       
MILWAUKEE — The Milwaukee Fire Department has been dispatched to the area of 22nd and Wisconsin Avenue for a death investigation. 
 
MFD was called out to the scene around 7:30 p.m. 
 
MFD officials say a person has died at that location. 
 
Officials with the Milwaukee County Medical Examiner’s Office confirm they have also been called out to the scene. 
 
FOX6 News has a crew en route, and we’re working to gather additional information. Monitor FOX6 News and FOX6Now.com for updates on this developing story.
